A visit paid to the cave in August 2021, revealed the cave partially flooded, with most conduits inaccessible. The main entrance gallery was filled with water, which was still forming a small lake outside the cave (Fig. 
34A
). Reaching the deepest areas inside the cave through the main entrance was impossible in that moment, but since there is another entrance in the middle of the cave (Figs 
34B
, 
35A
), the inner portions were accessible (Fig. 
35B
).
